'''貝德蘭姆立方'''（Bedlam cube）是由英國謎題專家布魯斯·貝德蘭姆設計的{{link-en|實體智力遊戲|Mechanical puzzle}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bedlampuzzles.com/13reasons.asp |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-05-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509092159/http://www.bedlampuzzles.com/13reasons.asp |archivedate=2008-05-09 }}: "Bruce Bedlam the Cubes inventor is putting all his royalty fees into his company 'Stonehenge Limited'"</ref><ref>[http://www.stonehenge.tv/intro.html Bruce's Theories] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stonehenge.tv/intro.html |date=20200223172932 }} — Stonehenge Ltd website</ref>。

== 設計 ==
貝德蘭姆立方由13個[[多立方體|多立方體]]組成，其中有十二個是五立方體，一個是四立方體。目的是將這十三個多立方體組成為一個4 x 4 x 4的立方體。在不考慮旋轉及鏡射的條件下，有19,186種不同的解答。

貝德蘭姆方塊的立方都比3 x 3 x 3的[[索馬立方|索馬立方]]要大一格，因此更不容易解。

== 歷史 ==
BBC《{{link-en|Dragons' Den|Dragons' Den (UK)}}》節目中的Rachel Elnaugh和Theo Paphitis，在第二季時要投資貝德蘭姆立方。他們願意為了貝德蘭姆立方股份的30%支付100,000英鎊。Danny Bamping（貝德蘭姆方塊背後的企業）最後選擇銀行的貸款而未選擇他們的投資，就如同在Dragons' Den節目的Where Are They Now內容中的一樣<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lammo.net/dragons-den/267/dragons-den-where-are-they-now-bedlam-cube/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-12-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302035534/http://www.lammo.net/dragons-den/267/dragons-den-where-are-they-now-bedlam-cube/ |archivedate=2013-03-02 }}: "A review on where are they now"</ref>。

== 紀錄 ==
[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]中最快組合貝德蘭姆立方的紀錄是由Danny Bamping在2006年11月9日創下，時間是11.03秒<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/records-5000/fastest-time-to-assemble-a-bedlam-cube-%28crazee-cube%29/ |title=Fastest time to assemble a Bedlam cube (Crazee Cube) |publisher=''Guinness World Records'' |accessdate=2013-11-06 |archive-date=2013-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210212837/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/records-5000/fastest-time-to-assemble-a-bedlam-cube-%28crazee-cube%29/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。蒙眼組合的最快紀錄是由Aleksandr Iljasov在2008年2月25日創下，時間是27.21秒<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/records-5000/fastest-time-to-assemble-a-bedlam-cube-%28crazee-cube%29-blindfolded/ |title=Fastest time to assemble a Bedlam cube (Crazee Cube) blindfolded |publisher=''Guinness World Records'' |accessdate=2013-11-06 |archive-date=2014-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826114910/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/records-5000/fastest-time-to-assemble-a-bedlam-cube-(crazee-cube)-blindfolded/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

